s well as clinics, research institutes and home fitness companies. NeurCG NeurCG provides cutting-edge AI-based graphics technologies and services that produce realistic human faces. It aims to revolutionize various industries by leveraging their advanced AI capabilities to generate highly realistic human faces, offering innovative and intelligent services to their clients. EndoSurge EndoSurge provides robotic interventional tools compatible with existing clinical magnetic reasonance imaging (MRI) scanners. This extends surgeons' capabilities by enabling radiation-free and image-guided treatment of heart disease for improved patient outcomes. Ventus Technologies Ventus Technologies specializes in high-resolution weather forecasts and nowcasts for roads, enhancing the safety and efficiency of electric and autonomous vehicles. Utilizing advanced physical downscaling and AI, the start-up delivers precise, location-specific weather data. It also helps car makers and fleet operators integrate these into exisiting range and consumption estimation systems. In joining the Cyber Valley Start-up Network, these five start-ups enhance the diversity and collaborative culture of the Cyber Valley Community. We are pleased to have them on board! Paul-David Bittner Business Development Manager Cyber Valley GmbH Start-up Network Related Articles 21.06.2024 Cyber Valley: World's first ELLIS Institute opens Cyber Valley entering the next phase with new partners 20.06.2024 Excellence meets capital: Deep Tech & Investor Day brings... Cyber Valley Days show the technological AI competitiveness of the state, the federal g... 19.06.2024 The AI Festival in Baden-Württemberg: Cyber Valley Days B... Cyber Valley Days 2024: Three days full of AI innovations and networking Cyber Valley Newsletter We send out an overview of the most important news and events in the Cyber Valley Community. Only available in English. Privacy Policy Register Register www.CleverReach.de Cyber Valley Cyber Valley Heis